function Start(snoQuest, idActorFollower)

-- Roina calls to investgate the river
	local idQuestOwner = Hydra.QuestGetOwner()
	
	Hydra.ActorPlayConversation(CON_SEARCH, idQuestOwner, idActorFollower)
	
end

function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)

--Move Roina follower to river
	idFollower = Hydra.QuestGetFollower(ID_ROINA_FOLLOWER)
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idFollower) then
		Hydra.QuestFollowerTakeOwnership(idFollower)
		Hydra.QActorEnableAI(idFollower, false)
		Hydra.ActorPlayConversation(CON_Victim, idSelf, idFollower)
		Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idFollower, LOC_RIVER, "IGC_NPC_RUN", true)
		Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(idFollower, LOC_RIVER)
	end
	Hydra.WaitForConversationFinished(CON_Victim)
	Hydra.QActorDelete(idFollower)
	-- Cecil taken by Wight effect
	Hydra.ActorPlaySound(LOC_WIGHTWATER, "Play_QUE_Generic_Scream_Male")
	--Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(LOC_WIGHTWATER, "drowned_seahag_geyser")
	Hydra.ActorSetPowerEffectSize(LOC_WIGHTWATER, 2.0)
	Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(LOC_WIGHTWATER, "drowned_seahag_geyser_damage")
	
-- Active Wight hair appearance
	Hydra.QActorAnim(GIZ_Hair, "AnimKey_Opening")
end

function Start(idActorNPC, sConversation, idActorPlayer)
	idClone = Hydra.CreatePersonalClone(ID_ROINA_RH_02)
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idClone) then
		Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idClone, LOC_ROINARUNTO, "npc_run", true)
		Hydra.QActorDeletePersonalClone(idClone, 1.0)
	end
end

function Start()
	-- Roina comments on Hair
	Hydra.QActorPlayConversation(CON_HAIR_BARK, idSelf, ID_ROINA_RH_02)
end
